            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Rissolfus"
                            >Rixsolfus</name></persName> indignus <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>
                        <foreign>pro anima e su invito dei genitori dona</foreign> Domino et <rs
                            key="#Churches">eclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Private_foundations">beate Sancte Marie semper
                            virginis et beati Sancti Donati episcopi confessoris</orgName>, quem nos
                        in proprio territurio nostro a fundamenta fabricis <rs
                            key="#Private_foundations">construximus</rs> (…) consentientem mihi
                        domno pater meus <persName key="#Abbots"><name ref="Raginulfus"
                                >Regnolfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <foreign>offre alle suddette chiese</foreign> quem pater meus aedificabet
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">omnem substantia nostra</rs> in qualibe
                        loco quecumque habere visuris sumus, <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine"
                        >vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Oil">olivetis</rs>, <rs key="#Acorns">silvis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Chestnuts">castanietis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis,
                            pascuis</rs>, culto vel inculto, <rs key="#Slave_labour">serbi et
                            ancille</rs>, <rs key="#Horses">cavallis</rs>, <rs key="#Cows"
                            >bovis</rs>, (…) in tali enim tenore (…) ut dum ego Rixsolfus presbitero
                        in hoc seculo vivere meruero, et dum mater mea <persName><name
                                ref="Luciberga">Luciperga</name></persName> et dilectissime tres
                        sorores mee <persName><name ref="Christina">Christina</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Raginpincta">Regnipincta</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Plaita">Plaita</name></persName> vivere
                        meruerimus, in nostra serbamus potestatem ipse iamdicte Dei ecclesie
                        studendum et res ipsorum ad usufructuandum et secundum Deum ad ipsa sancta
                        loca caste et iuste serbiendum et vivendum (…) Similiter in mea potestate
                        reserbo CL soledis pro anima patris mei dando de res nostras et C soledis
                        pro anima matris mee dando; et duodecim <rs key="#Slave">hominis</rs> pro
                        anima nostra <rs key="#Freedman">ad libertandum</rs>. <foreign>Si riserva
                            anche il diritto di nominare</foreign> rectorem et gubernatorem qui post
                        decesso matris mee et tribus sororis mee ipse Dei ecclesie miminere dibeas
                        et gubernare. <foreign>Vivrà con la madre e le sorelle. Se morisse prima di
                            averlo fatto, morte la madre e le sorelle</foreign>, <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs> nostre <placeName key="#Cities #Bishops"
                            ref="#places/4">Lucense</placeName> potestatem habeas in iamdicte
                        ecclesie Sancte Marie et Sancti Donati (…) in ambas <rs key="#Priests"
                            >presbitero</rs> uno ordinare qui secundum Dei precetum vivam et per
                        omnem septimanam tres diebus XXIIII pauperi prandere dibeas; prandium eorum
                        tali sit per omnem septimana: scaphilo grano <rs key="#Bread">pane</rs>
                        cocto, et duo congia <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs>, et duo congia de
                        pulmentario, <rs key="#Legumes">faba</rs> et <rs key="#Minores">panico</rs>
                        mixto, bene spisso et condito de uncto aut de <rs key="#Oil">oleo</rs>.
                            <foreign>Pena per gli eredi che contestassero quanto disposto:
                            maledizione e</foreign> soledis mille episcopi qui tunc fuerit. (…)
                        Actum <placeName ref="#places/4">Lucam</placeName>.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: + Rixsolfus presbitero; (ss)
                        Rignolfus abbas <foreign>fa scrivere al figlio </foreign>quia ego pro
                        egretudine mea non potuit scribere; (ss) <persName key="#Witness #Priests"
                                ><name ref="Agibrandus">Agiprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>; (ss) <persName key="#Witness #Priests"
                                ><name ref="Maginpertus">Magnipert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Ragibertus"
                            >Rachipertu</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Aunualdus"
                            >Aunualdus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName
                            key="#Writer #Priests"><name ref="Rissolfus">Rixsolfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
